textContent:
---batang ama/ina---

Hello bby!! Ngayon lang ako nakapag sulat kase pano ba naman. We had our first pregnancy scare BWAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA. Congratulations! Not pregnant! HAHAHAHAA ABABABAYUUU.

Though looking back, the funny thing is, di naman talaga siya scare kase di ka pa namab delayed. Jusq ang hirap pag nagsama dalawang OA no? HAHAHAHAHAH

Anyways, what happened just made me realize how I'm really already set on living out the rest of my live with you! I love you so much and no matter what happens we'll be together forever! Ket next year man mabuo si unica or next next year pa or kahit ano. Basta we're a package deal!

---im always here for you---

And speaking of being a package deal, I just want you to know na I'm always here for you ket san ka man mapadpad carreer-wise. Sa america man or sg or ket saan man. I'll be with you no matter what stage you are in your life and I want you to feel even just the littlest bit of comfort in knowing na kahit di pa tayo kasal, sasamahan parin kita sa hirap man o sa ginhawa. MWAAA!
